divs: Sighting DetailsWhile taking pictures of the night sky on Saturday, May 16, 2009 betwee 8:00pm and 9:00pm Mountain Time I found this triangle. I was using zoom and the line following the triangle craft is what the camera captured while the shutter was open. Unfortunately I was not using a tripod at the time, therefore the uneven looking line indicating travel of the craft. I was using a Nikon S630 with Night Landscape scene. I did not realize this object was captured until reviewing the files the next day.
Summary: Triangle High Up captured on Digital Camera
